   "body" : "![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1530283/113121345-24a31b80-9245-11eb-876b-7197fe803861.png)\r\nI've been testing a node with a maxmempool of 50MB, as as you can see, at around 6:40am the mempool reduces to zero due to continuing to filter out the lower fee transactions.\r\nI think the feefilter reduction needs to therefore take into account the maxmempool setting and decrease faster for nodes with a small maxmempool.",
